https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F329cOvM.png&h=8697482f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nC行將A B行夾埋做一個字，然後F行countif睇下有無Yes出現過..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:48:42.000Z","msg":"唔該ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:15:58.000Z","msg":"亦可以直接用countifs<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec72305edb4dd0858faca1ac42b4c31b535ff299","tid":1788262,"uid":71237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fdf97b4224c3551cdc664995b6f4f1095d1250bb","tid":1788262,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"首先用for loop由A2掃落A16<br />\n檢查如果人名無喺Column D出現過就抄value去Column D, E<br />\n如果出現過就再加多一個if, 如果Column B係Yes就出Yes"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T15:20:06.000Z","msg":"我已經寫完，測試過無問題。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">Sub lihkg()\nColACount = Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(1048575, 1).End(xlUp).Row\n\nFor i = 2 To ColACount\n    ColDCount = Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(1048575, 4).End(xlUp).Row\n    ExistColD = False\n    For j = 2 To ColDCount\n        If Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(i, 1) = Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(j, 4) Then\n            ExistColD = True\n            If Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(i, 2) = &quot;Yes&quot; Then\n                Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(j, 5) = &quot;Yes&quot;\n            End If\n        End If\n    Next j\n    If ExistColD = False Then\n        Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(ColDCount + 1, 4) = Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(i, 1)\n        Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(ColDCount + 1, 5) = Worksheets(&quot;Sheet1&quot;).Cells(i, 2)\n    End If\nNext i\nEnd Sub</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n如果完全唔識點用VBA，可以由依條片第35秒開始睇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/GOPNlVrcVW8?list=PLHguOF-Fnm4xZmDj4Kc5ZSGQOo0R44Ek-&amp;t=36\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu